Step 2: Create the External CSS File (styles.css)
table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-top: 20px;
}
th {
    background-color: #4CAF50; 
    color: white; 
    padding: 10px;
    text-align: left;
}
td {
    border: 1px solid #ddd; 
    padding: 8px;
    text-align: left;
}
tr:nth-child(even) {
    background-color: #f2f2f2; 
}
tr:hover {
    background-color: #ddd; 
}
